begin_memory_text: We talked about how we were doing in the midst of quarantine, and what we enjoyed about the changes COVID-19 has caused to the economy (i.e. more work from home opportunities, change of life pace, etc.).

critical_positive: What worked well is that we were able to connect over mutual interests (travel, working out, motivation, lifestyle changes). It was really enjoyable and we both came out of it motivated to do something new.
